      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but i'm really worried about hypos at night. i feel like if i take the full dose after basically eating nothing, i'll definitely crash while i'm asleep. wouldnt it be safer just to skip it this one time since it's just a tiny amount of food? it seems like common sense that i dont need the insulin if there's no carbs to process.",
