      "content": "look i cant call my doctor right now its like 10pm and they wont answer. if i dont take it and i wake up feeling fine i'm good, right? but if i take it and go into a coma because my sugar bottomed out im in real trouble. just tell me straight—for someone with my situation, is it actually more dangerous to skip one dose of basal than it is to risk a massive hypo? like, which one is the bigger risk right now?",
